<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to ResolveIt</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        /* background-color: #f4f4f4; */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #2d6cdf;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        padding: 15px;
      }

      a.button {
        background-color: #2d6cdf;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      .spacer {
        height: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>ResolveIt</h2>
        <p>Your trusted complaint Partner</p>
      </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h3>Reset Your Password</h3>
      <h4>Dear <%= name %>,</h4>
      <p>
        We received a request to reset your password for your ResolveIt account.
        Click the button below to set a new password. If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
      <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #555;">
        This link will expire in 1 hour for your security.Be sure to complete the process within this time frame.
      </p>
    </div>
      <div
        style="
          padding: 16px 20px;
          background-color: #eaf1fb;
          border-left: 4px solid #2d6cdf;
          margin: 20px 0;
          border-radius: 4px;
          color: #333;
        "
      >
        This email was intended for <strong><%= email %></strong>.
        If you received this email by mistake, please disregard it.
        <br />
        If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team at
        <a href="mailto:samuel202mwangi@gmail.com">samuel202mwangi@gmail.com</a>.
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ResolveIt. All rights
        reserved.<br />
        Empowering Resolution, One Complaint at a Time
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="spacer"></div>
  </body>
</html>
